The RDL-TDC can be implemented both in ASIC and FPGA; however, since the
 latter does not allow compensation mechanisms to correct PVT variations,
 required to have matching in the duration of the generated clock periods,
 the ASIC approach is more suitable for this architecture.
\end_layout

